{"tid":1948300,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不如黎多次一人一信支持港台？","createTime":"2020-03-29T02:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T11:11:41.000Z","uid":6003,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"98b47379686bac67e75466ea6c8532b399a7cb4a","tid":1948300,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><em>[王喜忠勇毅]全部人同我一人一信表揚港台!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1882458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1882458</a></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次港台玩咁大<br />\n令到WHO喺全世界面前出醜<br />\n可以預期港共會繼續打壓港台<br />\n得閒就派爪牙去廣播道搞事<br />\n又寫信投訴呢樣嗰樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我地不如先幫港台打定底，再次一人一信支持港台同The Pulse節目？<br />\n<br />\nemail內容盡可能原創<br />\n亦可基於上面條link加以修改<br />\n<br />\nemail: ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n又或者咁講<br />\n其實除左CLS<br />\n我地一有時間就應該send email表揚港台<br />\n每次只係用你五至十分鐘<br />\n成本咁低點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當鼓勵港台上下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96db914678ddd6b4490bc0d1e61d766b13a6f25e","tid":1948300,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42cdaefbfb80148b3a9626995ba94419cdaacf0a","tid":1948300,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69e53e00759ce3e1d6a79a89b7900cdb41bc4274","tid":1948300,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"真 可惜暫時唔可以去門口表揚"},{"pid":"73599f5e5a43d3a79f75daa017db41726e1ce3f5","tid":1948300,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd7fe99967abcd4dbfbb549b25161e7aa868340","tid":1948300,